1414
01:14:56,162 --> 01:14:57,043
Ciao.

1415
01:14:57,064 --> 01:14:57,384
Buongiorno.

1416
01:14:57,623 --> 01:14:58,024
Buongiorno.

1417
01:14:58,823 --> 01:15:00,385
Allora, novità?

